{"tid":2214336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康籲國際合作抗中共侵港人自由　華府顧問指香港是中共徹底失敗的「華麗實驗」","createTime":"2020-09-23T07:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T08:36:35.000Z","uid":53379,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc903670fa07189fb12c6b8c4f62b7a930960a94","tid":2214336,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">彭定康籲國際合作抗中共侵港人自由　華府顧問指香港是中共徹底失敗的「華麗實驗」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後一任港督彭定康香港時間周二 (9 月 22 日) 晚上出席網上論壇時再指出，中共近期對香港的行動是廿一世紀中，對任何城市的自由 (freedom) 以及自主 (liberty) 作最大侵犯。他又呼籲所有民主國家共同努力捍衛自由。<br />\n<br />\n該網上論壇由加拿大智庫 Macdonald Laurier 研究所主持，並與香港觀察、歐洲安全政策價值觀中心等合作舉辦，出席論壇的除了有彭定康，亦包括香港眾志前主席羅冠聰、美國國務院中國政策首席顧問余茂春、德國馬歇爾基金會研究員馬曉月 (Mareike Ohlberg) 、香港觀察創辦人羅哲斯 (Benedict Rogers) 等人，以討論自由世界將如何應對北京鎮壓，尤其香港的前途問題。<br />\n<br />\n........<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%B7%E7%B1%B2%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E4%BE%B5%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-%E8%8F%AF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F%E6%8C%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%BE%B9%E5%BA%95%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E7%9A%84-%E8%8F%AF%E9%BA%97%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97/?fbclid=IwAR17xZRc0SLubFU9hjCH-1m_6rcMu0eS7R0k8EMm1dVRCDQ5zaQvNqO0RoA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258A%2597%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%25BE%25B9%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597%25E7%259A%2584-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%25BA%2597%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR17xZRc0SLubFU9hjCH-1m_6rcMu0eS7R0k8EMm1dVRCDQ5zaQvNqO0Ro